        Powered by <a href="https://pyodide.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Pyodide</a>,
        <a href="https://github.com/nicowillis/JSCPP" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">JSCPP</a>
        &amp; <a href="https://sql.js.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">SQL.js</a>
